%1* Singing Jelly Baby

First build the circuit (see below), then do ^this stuff^ from the "command
line":

# create a work directory
  - ^mkdir work^
  - ^cd work^
# install Wiring Pi
  - ^wget -O wp.deb -r tinyurl.com/wiringpi^
  - ^sudo dpkg -i wp.deb^
# get the code
  - ^wget -O jb.sh -r tinyurl.com/pijellybaby^
  - ^chmod +x jb.sh^
# get the sound effects
  - ^wget -O police.wav -r tinyurl.com/policewav^
# run the thing
  - ^sudo ./jb.sh^


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
%1* Traffic Lights

First build the circuit (see below), then do ^this stuff^ from the "command
line":

# get the code
  - ^wget -O TrafficLED.py -r tinyurl.com/pitraffic^
  - ^cat TrafficLED.py^
# run the thing
  - ^sudo python TrafficLED.py^


